    "excerpt": "This is an annually updated chart that I have been creating and sharing for 10+ years. This grid for counting the omer includes the secular date for 2026 as well as Hebrew dates and the sefirot associated with each day of the omer. More information can be found on my <a href=\"https://count.omerjourney.net/\">website</a>.",
    "content": "<p><strong>DOWNLOAD:</strong> <a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Days-of-the-Omer-5786-2026-Karen-Levine-2026.pdf\">PDF</a></p>\n<p>This is an updated version of a chart that I have been creating and sharing for 10+ years. This grid for counting the omer includes the secular date for 2025 as well as Hebrew dates and the sefirot associated with each day of the omer. More information can be found on my <a href=\"https://count.omerjourney.net/\">website</a>.</p>\n<hr />\n<div id=\"attachment_66872\" style=\"width: 2210px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/days-of-the-omer-5786-2026-karen-levine-2026.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-66872\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/days-of-the-omer-5786-2026-karen-levine-2026.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2200\" height=\"1700\" class=\"size-full wp-image-66872\" srcset=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/days-of-the-omer-5786-2026-karen-levine-2026.png 2200w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/days-of-the-omer-5786-2026-karen-levine-2026-300x232.png 300w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/days-of-the-omer-5786-2026-karen-levine-2026-1024x791.png 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 2200px) 100vw, 2200px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-66872\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Days of the Omer 5786-2026 (Karen Levine 2026)</p></div>\n<p><strong>Previous years:</strong> <a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Omer-grid-5785-Karen-Levine-2025.pdf\">2025</a>, <a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Omer-grid-5784-Karen-Levine-2024.pdf\">2024</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
